---

## 1. Project Overview

HostelGate is a gate management system for NIT Goa that digitizes the campus entry/exit process. It serves three user types:

| User | Platform | Purpose |
|------|----------|---------|
| **Students** | Android APK | Generate QR codes for entry/exit, apply for leave |
| **Wardens** | Android APK | Approve/reject leave applications and extensions |
| **Security Guards** | Separate app (Security Portal) | Scan QR codes at the gate |
| **iOS Users** | Web (Safari) | Same as above, via https://nit-goa-gate-system.web.app |

